 class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUES</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'::1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'root'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">